name: DYRTxTRELLExK-DUBB (PAIN) NFT
description: This song speaks about real life pain from artist DYRT and K-DUBB. This is my first amateur video completely edited on TikTok and shot with a iPhone 12 Pro Max.The first half of the video was shot on Rarity Mountain in Tennessee on I-75. The second half was shot in Atlanta on my way home to Florida.I speak about me finding my first cousin dead in my mothers basement when I was 18 and how I still have dreams about the experience to this day. I also talk about my daughter dying from heart failure in 2013 and how it effected my life.The lyrics in this song are %100 real. This is a testimony of the pain I’ve felt in my life but only covers a small portion of the whole story.
